title: Aggregation of DEA Clandestine Labs, California into California Zip Code Boundaries
name: Aggregation of DEA Clandestine Labs, California into California Zip Code Boundaries
description: We took some of the DEA's reported drug seizure information, geocoded, and saved it as KML.  This is a subset  that represents clandestine labs in one state: California.Looking for hot spots of drug production.
